.TH "tomoyo_path_permission" 9 "tomoyo_path_permission" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tomoyo_path_permission \- Check permission for single path operation.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" tomoyo_path_permission
.BI "(struct tomoyo_request_info *r "  ","
.BI "u8 operation "  ","
.BI "const struct tomoyo_path_info *filename "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "r" 12
Pointer to "struct tomoyo_request_info".
.IP "operation" 12
Type of operation.
.IP "filename" 12
Filename to check.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns 0 on success, negative value otherwise.

Caller holds \fBtomoyo_read_lock\fP.
